{"id": 231953954, "title": "FLUCTUATING GLOBAL SUGAR PRICES HITTING LOCAL PRODUCERS", "text": "The Ubombo Sugar Limited (USL) Head of Corporate Affairs Leonard Ndzimandze has lamented on the fluctuation of sugar prices in the global markets. Ndzimandze shared that these prices were the current sore point for the company as the prices have taken a dip. He stated that over the period of six months, the prices of sugar had dropped significantly. \u201cThat is definitely going to take a knock on our bottom line,\u201d he said. Ndzimandze shared that the main drivers for the fluctuation of prices were the demand and the supply. He shared that countries like Brazil were looking into increasing their sugar production volumes this season.", "summary": "BIG BEND &ndash; The fluctuating global sugar prices have continued to be the thorn in the flesh for the local sugar industry. &nbsp;\nThe Ubombo Sugar", "url": "http://www.times.co.sz/business/145518-fluctuating-global-sugar-prices-hitting-local-producers.html", "image": null, "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 12:45:00", "author": null, "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "sz", "sentiment": -0.348}